I had dinner at Caffe Boa this past Wednesday. Amazing atmosphere and vibe, very classy and elegant.  We had the Salsiccia Contadina as an appetizer and it was delicious. Very large portion for a starter.  For our entres we had the Chicken special. Good but no overly impressive. We also had the Voodoo Penne. The Penne was absolutely phenomenal.   I was very impressed with the service, Bethany was great. I will surely return soon and recommend you do as well.

