We took in the World Cup Final here on Sunday with a few friends.   The beer selection is off the charts. Loved the San Tan Epicenter. We had the Pretzel with Beer Sauce as well, delicious and good to share. Last we had the Haus Brat and the Spicy Brat. Their homemade sauerkraut was off the charts as a topping.   The game was slow but the people and staff were fun and charming. Certainly a place we will be visiting again and again.  Only drawback is the size of the bar area - a little cramped.

